Package javax0.wtf

Interface Function

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    Condition, PostFunction, PreFunction, Validator
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    FalseCondition, FalseValidator, NullPreFunction, OkPostFunction, SampleCondition, SamplePostFunction, SamplePreFunction, SampleValidator, TrueCondition, TrueValidator

    public interface Function
    The methods that are common for actions, conditions, pre functions and post functions.

    Note that the work flow engine may reuse objects that implement this interface. In other words the methods have to be thread safe.

    Author:
    Peter Verhas
